{"id": "1423562702504202240", "channel_id": "1423562702504202240", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果，我是说如果，\n如果有一天融蚀消失了，世界会变成什么样？弥萨格大学会变成什么样？\n\n“呼——守密人，你愣着做什么，快过来呀！”\n钟声、彩带、欢笑、乐音，大学里正举办着热闹的社团迎新活动。\n闲逛一圈，就被唤醒体塞了一堆招新海报：“章鱼章鱼我们喜欢你”🤔、“甜品猎人”😮、“触手的诱惑”😲……\n守密人想加入哪位唤醒体的社团？如果是你会组织什么有趣的社团~\n\n✨ 特别活动「如果一切如常」，将于10月6日 9:00 - 10月20日 9:00 开启！\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\nIf, I'm saying if,\nIf one day Dissolution disappeared, what would the world be like? What would Mythag University become?\n\n\"Phew—Keeper, why are you standing there? Come on!\"\nWith bells, ribbons, laughter, and music, the university is hosting a boisterous club welcome event. \nAfter wandering around, you're bombarded by Awakeners with recruitment posters: \"Octopus Octopus We Like You\" 🤔, \"Dessert Hunters\" 😮, \"Temptation of Tentacles\" 😲…\nSo, which Awakener's club would you like to join, Keeper? And if it were you, what fun club would you organize?\n\n✨ Special Event \"If Life Was As Usual\" available from <t:1759712400:F> to <t:1760922000:F>!", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T06:49:56.793000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "spend", "emoji_id": "1356086121888747531", "count": 29}, {"emoji": "drool", "emoji_id": "1356053063139463248", "count": 18}, {"emoji": "wow", "emoji_id": "1356053147029864518", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "satisfy", "emoji_id": "1400771690321154110", "count": 6}, {"emoji": "angry1", "emoji_id": "1356053023272599668", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1423562702835548260", "filename": "1--.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1356336, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423562702504202240/1423562702835548260/1--.jpg?ex=69ccc014&is=69cb6e94&hm=cc9ea25d9ca5ba84eaf8aad8225143a98583ad162bfc19d04b87ab9758f1fe98&"}, {"id": "1423562703225487401", "filename": "2-4-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 918539, "url": "https://cdn.disco